\pandocbounded{\includegraphics[keepaspectratio,alt={Bar Chart Comparing Accuracy and AUC Across Inline Models}]{/Users/cantabile/projects/sit/csc3105/csc3105-project/plots/09_model_comparison.png}}
\caption{Bar Chart Comparing Accuracy and AUC Across Inline Models}
\end{figure}

A grouped bar chart provides a clean side-by-side comparison of accuracy
and AUC for the inline tabular models and ensemble variants. The
separate CNN+Transformer result should be read from Table 1 rather than
interpreted as part of the same plotted benchmark.

\begin{itemize}
\tightlist
\item
  The plotted inline models are evaluated on the imbalanced expanded
